{"tid":1276962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【建制派內鬨】與謝偉俊口角 何君堯：你唔需要lecture我","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:23:59.000Z","uid":33643,"like":65,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b97b5476e25f995ec9d69e8420c9c2492d964854","tid":1276962,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"【建制派內鬨】與謝偉俊口角 何君堯：你唔需要lecture我<br />\n<br />\n民主派及建制派議員先後在立法會外記者時。民主派議員見記者期間，建制派何君堯在一旁高聲指責他們，「你班厚顏無恥，假仁假義，唔好聽個班廢柴講嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊在一旁勸說何君堯，「你咁樣我地唔會同你一齊見（記者）」，何君堯說，「我無話同你一齊見阿 Paul。」面露不滿的謝偉俊，轉身離開。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯則反斥，「you may just go away and walk away from Hong Kong.你唔需要lecture我，lecture 嗰班友仔。」<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6774282ae236cc464a4679425f4febcd8967d6a","tid":1276962,"uid":23815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"邊個係律師界大粒啲呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"01a3e94b2f37bfc80315f3dd0c0bcb80292bd840","tid":1276962,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:38:31.000Z","msg":"正, 最鐘意睇到呢D"},{"pid":"d55f51caf390103462109bb437da991ba88caa08","tid":1276962,"uid":262480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c665ff59c56aa62e8e5d2724bdf7bed446e18c6e","tid":1276962,"uid":76046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"去片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2281296901955917?s=1602852373&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2281296901955917%3Fs%3D1602852373%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bre6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=98909cde\" tar